name: CBSA designated ports of entry/inland offices
description:
One or a combination of these types of CBSA office:
- Air Ports of Entry
- Land Ports of Entry
- Marine Ports of Entry
- All Ports of Entry (Air, Land and Marine)
- Inland Offices
- Total - CBSA Land, Air and Marine port of entry and Inland Offices
